                                <h2 class="hf2 title">Kids Ministry</h2>
                                <div class="description">
                                    <p>Statistics and studies say that the most important learning and development stage for a child is 0-5 years. We take this very seriously hence we start teaching our kids the truths about life and God as early as 3 years. Each lesson prepared by our volunteers communicates to the kids in a creative way the truths about God and also satisfies the eminent “WHY” question lobbed by our little ones.<br><br>No matter how old your children are, we have a program for them. Kids aged 0-3 years are tenderly looked after in the crèche. Kids aged 4-7 years are loved and taught the ways of our almighty God through the stories and activities. And kids aged 8-11 years are taught through the Bible and are encouraged to live out their faith more consciously and deliberately.<br><br>Proverbs 22:6 says, “Train up a child in the way he should go; even when he is old he will not depart from it.” We would love to teach your kids about worship, ethics, and morality through the word of God in the most fun way.<br>Join us!!</p>
