                                <h2 class="hf2 title">Men's Ministry</h2>
                                <div class="description">
                                    <p>Navigating the rapids on a turbulent river is only possible by being attentive to the navigator’s directions and being in sync with the team. Similarly navigating the rapids of life without direction and alone is a difficult and even a dangerous undertaking. DBF Central’s men’s ministry is all about pursuing to be the men after God’s own heart, ready to do the will of God, by being attentive to God’s direction and being in sync with the men around.<br><br>Our events provide for opportunities to navigate most relevant and most turbulent topics known to men along with the help of experienced and skilled trainers. We don’t just believe in learning in a conference setting but more so out in the open while sweating it out. Don’t worry; we do the most rational endeavors known, like playing cricket in our church compound under the blazing sun, paint ball shooting, praying while driving and rafting at Rishikesh. We would hate to see you miss out on these relevant and rational adventures.</p>
